{"tid":703373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[洋腸變偽臘腸]42歲大媽扮法國型男 呃37歲港女80萬元","createTime":"2018-06-15T16:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T14:53:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"52fd5b0c77452bf4ae2222c2005baef71b2eaa9e","tid":703373,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"一名37歲本地女子於上月24日報案，指於2017年12月透過手機應用程式認識一名自稱為法國及新加坡混血兒、在法國從事室內設計的男子，兩人之後疑發展網上情緣，期間該名男子聲稱工作上遇到財務問題，向報案人索取金錢。報案人遂按指示於今年2至4月期間，先後多次將共約80萬港元存入6個本地銀行戶口。其後，報案人與該名男子失去聯絡，懷疑受騙。<br />\n<br />\n經反詐騙協調中心協調後，灣仔警區刑事調查隊探員昨日(14日)在中區拘捕該名<span style=\"color: red;\">42歲姓莫的內地女子</span>，涉嫌「以欺騙手段取得財產」。初步調查顯示，被捕女子為其中一個本地銀行戶口的持有人，她已獲准保釋候查，須於八月中旬向警方報到。 <br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/photo/bkn-20180615124052508-0615_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180615202703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180615%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180615124052508-0615_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180615202703&d=j%2BGigg9e8pTkALk91wtY67IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=da506ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/photo/bkn-20180615124052508-0615_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180615202703</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/bkn-20180615124052508-0615_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180615%2Fbkn-20180615124052508-0615_00822_001.html&d=j%2BGigg9e8pTkALk91wtY67IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7c67cd9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/bkn-20180615124052508-0615_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8f5029f75aa58b858e98f636db93d2a339d2439f","tid":703373,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"慘囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a2b208cd0a12b1885b97ce58a3586f9fb1a44f","tid":703373,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score